            Nominum is a high technology company who leverages network traffic and big data to do some amazing things online. I worked with
            Nominum product owners and their Internet Service Provider customers to rethink how internet traffic can be used to do things like help parents block
            sensitive content or even help ISPs contact their customers in browser in the case of a planned outage.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

